data.description: Garage Lover's Dream! Attached 4.5 car garage connected to a 40 x 50 heated building with 12" high clearance. The attached home includes a family room featuring a stone fireplace open to the kitchen. 2 bedrooms and 1 and 1/2 bath. Laundry room/ utility room contains the mechanics for the home. The home and the garages are very well insulated. This property is Zoned  Business but being used as a residential property currently. Endless possibilities for a business and lots of room to expand. Please verify any intended business use with Green Township Zoning.  Use your imagination! Selling AS IS. Septic and Well text has been ordered. Set of garage doors closest to the home do not work.  Schedule your private showing today.
